sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant MAX as MAX Platform
  participant B1 as Bot1 (Producer)
  participant DB as SQLite (/var/lib/max-bot1/bot.db)
  participant B2 as Bot2 (Dispatch Worker)
  participant TG as Telegram Bot API

  MAX->>B1: inbound message webhook
  B1->>B1: normalize + build notify_text
  B1->>DB: INSERT events (fact)
  B1->>DB: INSERT delivery (tasks: TG + MAX)
  Note over B1,DB: Bot1 does not send, no retries

  loop dispatch loop
    B2->>DB: claim_batch (new -> processing, claim_id, claim_ts)
    alt lease timeout path
      B2->>DB: lease_timeout: processing(old claim_ts) -> new
      Note over B2,DB: log "lease_timeout released=.. lease_sec=.."
    end
    B2->>TG: sendMessage
    B2->>MAX: send to user_id
    alt success
      B2->>DB: set_status sent (attempts++)
      Note over B2,DB: claim_id must match DB to update exactly 1 row
    else error
      B2->>DB: attempts++ / retry or dead
    end
  end
